/-
The global expected value factors as a product of local expected values over
the prime factors of squarefree `q`.
-/
lemma globalMean_eq_prod_localMean (k : ℕ) (q : ℕ) [NeZero q] (hq : Squarefree q)
    (Ω : ∀ p : ℕ, Finset (ZMod p)) :
